prompt:
Research and compare the following options: {{OPTIONS}}

Comparison criteria: {{CRITERIA}}

For each option, provide:
1. Current version and maintenance status
2. Key features
3. Pros and cons
4. Best use cases
5. Community adoption (GitHub stars, npm downloads)
6. Score for each criterion (1-10)

Return results in JSON format:
{
  "comparison": [
    {
      "name": "<option-name>",
      "version": "<version>",
      "features": ["<feature1>", "<feature2>"],
      "pros": ["<pro1>", "<pro2>"],
      "cons": ["<con1>", "<con2>"],
      "stats": {
        "github_stars": <number>,
        "npm_weekly_downloads": "<number>"
      },
      "scores": {
        "<criterion1>": <1-10>,
        "<criterion2>": <1-10>
      }
    }
  ],
  "recommendation": {
    "choice": "<recommended-option>",
    "reasoning": "<why>"
  }
}
